name: iitm-network-auth-app
description: Cross platform application for authentication inside IIT Madras campus network

packageJSON.name: iitmnetworkauthapp
packageJSON.description: Cross platform application for authentication inside IIT Madras campus network.

scripts.release:osx: copyfiles -f dist/mac/*.{dmg,zip} release/osx && PACKAGE_VERSION=$(cat app/package.json | grep version | head -1 | awk -F: '{ print $2 }' | sed 's/[",]//g' | tr -d '[[:space:]]') && echo $PACKAGE_VERSION >> ./release/osx/VERSION

releases.name: v0.3.0
releases.body:
Stable release targeting Linux (`appimage`, `deb`, `tar.gz`), Windows (`exe`) and MacOS (`dmg`)
- Preserves login session as long as the app is open.
- Option to remember username/password.
- Automatic updates and update notification for manual updates.

releases.name: Initial release
releases.body: This is the initial release for IIT Madras Network Auth
